; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/gh-pr-view.md

% gh-pr-view, common

# View the pull request associated with the current branch
gh pr view

# View a specific pull request
gh pr view <123>

# Open the pull request in the default web browser
gh pr view <__w___web_>

# Show comments in the terminal
gh pr view <123> <__c___comments_>
